  "detailed_description": "<h1>IMPORTANT NOTE:</h1><p>**A webcam is required to play this game**</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/932f25f23ff821409ba41b207d1f5e67.poster.avif?t=1624015068\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/932f25f23ff821409ba41b207d1f5e67.webm?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/932f25f23ff821409ba41b207d1f5e67.mp4?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From the developer of Runster and Fitforce.<br><br>A fantasy adventure of a bear looking for delicious honey, but will he be able to complete his journey?<br><br>The forest is acting strange and the bees are evolving somehow, they are getting bigger and stronger but your tummy is growling so hard for something sweet. As a bear, you will have to overcome these bees to get your claw on yummy honey inside. Let's get moving, your tummy can't wait any longer!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Motion-sensing control through a webcam:</strong></h2>Use your body movement to attack the tree and fight angry bees until the beehive falls.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/9993b2df552f526670f755db2895a79b.poster.avif?t=1624015068\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/9993b2df552f526670f755db2895a79b.webm?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/9993b2df552f526670f755db2895a79b.mp4?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 Gameplay modes available:</strong></h2>train yourself and take on the challenges.<br><br><br>(1) <strong>Journey:</strong> Encounter a series of enemies, beat those bees. Complete the journey and eat the most delicious honey.<br><br>(2) <strong>Quick Fight:</strong> Short fight with the enemies you have encountered. Revisit them for fun or to train yourself for the rematch.<br><br>(3) <strong>Endless:</strong> Fight endless waves of stronger enemies. Every time you defeat the enemy, you can choose a new talent to upgrade and customize the play style in your way.<br>Your result will be recorded on the leaderboard, challenge yourself and become the strongest bear in the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/d43de4de126202ddbbbe44a3386098e9.poster.avif?t=1624015068\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/d43de4de126202ddbbbe44a3386098e9.webm?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/d43de4de126202ddbbbe44a3386098e9.mp4?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be cool or cute or whatever:</strong></h2>Customize your bear with costume and dance emotes received by completing stages in the game.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/13f5171c61007d6aacae6f94c3ecc811.poster.avif?t=1624015068\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/13f5171c61007d6aacae6f94c3ecc811.webm?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1593760/extras/13f5171c61007d6aacae6f94c3ecc811.mp4?t=1624015068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
